name: "Is This the NFT?”
description: The quickest and most convoluted video description of how to mint an NFT on the cheap. Tazos as a currency has been described to me as 'the dive bar' or even 'dumpster pizza' of the current hot block-chain currencies, quite decentralized maybe to a fault. So I thought I'd make something quick and dirty to reflect the punk vibe of all of this…  / / - - / / - - / / - - / /  Hopefully you find this NFT video less intimidating (not to mention when it doesn’t cost $300 to get involved) and possibly even useful. / / - - / / - - / / - - / / Other invisible details that are good to know specific to this Hic Et Nunc platform: Descriptions are limited to 2,000 characters including spaces, mp4 videos are limited to 40 mb, and wealth inequality is the most limiting quality of life.
